<h1>Nextcloud and Adfinis SyGroup sign strategic partnership</h1>
<p><strong>Stuttgart, May 9 2017.</strong> as new Nextcloud's sales and integration partner, Adfinis SyGroup is delivering its on-premise solution for the secure storage and management of data to the Swiss market. Together, Nextcloud and Adfinis SyGroup offer their customers full control over sensitive business data and a complete range of services for a carefree use of the storage, communication and collaboration solution in the daily working routine.</p>

<p>As part of the partnership, Adfinis SyGroup provides comprehensive integration and support services for the Open Source enterprise file sync and share, communication and collaboration solution Nextcloud. In so doing, Adfinis SyGroup expands its diverse portfolio of services for open source technologies and solutions.</p>

<blockquote>The partnership with Adfinis SyGroup gives our customers access to exclusive services and the broad know-how of the experienced open source experts from Switzerland</blockquote> says Frank Karlitschek, Managing Director and founder of Nextcloud. <blockquote>In the future, we are looking forward to implementing complex projects together with Adfinis SyGroup,in order to open up new paths to collaborative work with the highest quality and safety standards</blockquote>

<blockquote>From a strategic point of view, Nextcloud optimally complements the open source portfolio of Adfinis SyGroup."In terms of security, collaboration and user-friendliness, Nextcloud is unique among vendors for storage solutions</blockquote> explains  Nicolas Chistener, CEO of Adfinis SyGroup. <blockquote>Nextcloud is making tremendous advances and we are proud to be able to count another innovation leader from the open source world to our partners</blockquote>

<p>As a self-hosted storage solution, Nextcloud provides users with full control over the location and access rights of stored data. While Nextcloud guarantees maximum security for sensitive business data, Adfinis SyGroup ensures the uncomplicated migration of existing data into the cloud, seamlessly integrating Nextcloud into existing IT infrastructure enabling Nextcloud to be used in enterprise environments in the most effective and care-free way.</p>

<p>Amongst others, Nextcloud provides,  the following features:
<ul>
<li>Sync, share, and collaborate on files with colleagues, customers, and partners</li>
<li>Local and device independent usage via desktop, mobile device or web client</li>
<li>Centralized data access regardless of whether the data is on a local or external storage</li>
<li>Search, tagging and favorites function for the quick retrieval of information</li>
<li>Integrated Collaboration & Communication Tools: Collabora Online Office, Calendar & Contacts Apps, Audio & Video Services</li>
<li>Nextcloud clients for Android, iOS and desktop systems</li>
<li>Extensive monitoring, logging and enterprise-ready compliance tools to control and secure the flow of data</li>
<li>and much more</li>
</ul></p>

<p><strong>About Adfinis SyGroup AG</strong></br />
Since 2000, Adfinis SyGroup AG has been consistently active in the open source environment. At the three locations in Berne, Basel and Zurich, Adfinis SyGroup employs around 50 people today and has successfully established itself as a leading provider of open source technologies across Swiss borders.</br />
As a proven service provider and partner, Adfinis SyGroup supports clients from the private and public sectors in the planning, testing and implementation of tailor-made software projects. The core competences of Adfinis SyGroup AG are open source engineering & devops, 24/7 services & support, managed services and open source development.
Further information: <a href="https://adfinis-sygroup.ch/en">adfinis-sygroup.ch/en</a></p>

<p><strong>About Nextcloud</strong></br />
Nextcloud offers a unique-in-the-industry fully open source solution for on-premise data handling and communication with an uncompromising focus on security and privacy. Nextcloud brings together universal access to data with next-generation secure communication and collaboration capabilities under direct control of IT and integrated with existing compliant infrastructure. Nextcloud's open, modular architecture, emphasis on security and advanced federation capabilities enable modern enterprises to leverage their existing assets within and across the borders of their organization. For more information, visit <a href="https://nextcloud.com">https://nextcloud.com</a> or follow <a href="https://twitter.com/nextclouders">@Nextclouders on Twitter.</a></p>

